>\n<br />\n「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你在對香港議員說三道四，被白眼。」<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「說議員濫權不能算干涉&hellip;&hellip;一國原則！&hellip;&hellip;表態的事，能算干涉嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n接連便是難懂的話，什麼「香港自古以來是中國的一部份」，什麼「大國勃起」之類，引得衆人都鬨笑起來，店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"9e8a0c2679e8107b2b0e299cd8d322165a53a288","tid":1973192,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:14:19.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"ab0c9f49465f2931ef2b885689bd128d8472db5a","tid":1973192,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:14:31.000Z","msg":"我既國家得香港"},{"pid":"e1dcd0bc5cb3cb69f974d9af30c28a5bdb3899a7","tid":1973192,"uid":6799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"敵人反對的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b8f458d436a04c989d3f9ce4f0d8993eb27b0a","tid":1973192,"uid":31151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:15:01.000Z","msg":"你國家安唔安全關我撚事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed03bdd2fd628d396c1264b15bc586954b6f3573","tid":1973192,"uid":41821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:16:32.000Z","msg":"支那狗幾時死全家?"},{"pid":"1aa896bb2e9c5ee81765228e323f7ae5c0741f77","tid":1973192,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:18:41.000Z","msg":"支那國太危險，國咩家安全意識<br />\n要有危機意識先啱"},{"pid":"784af45004fd3181cbb77e2b20f0d0cd843fc670","tid":1973192,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e7e76058b39cda09bf8b014342206869ee6e23","tid":1973192,"uid":254450,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"4ffba7f03cc77898f153a13c0e5dd440b47bbb6d","tid":1973192,"uid":55955,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:05:31.000Z","msg":"諗起蕭生話佢會行溫和路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\